    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable and comfortable driving experience. The exterior finish remains vibrant, though a close inspection may reveal minor surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with all features and electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid, providing a smooth ride and steady performance that makes it an excellent choice for a daily driver or long-distance travel.",
